snippet.title: Maxwell's World Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
http://www.nexusmods.com/fallout4/mods/18949/?

When a rescue mission goes awry, the Sole Survivor finds themselves trapped in a very large, very haunted amusement park. Now, they must avoid temptation, skeleton armies, and the machinations of Mister Maxwell if they wish to escape with their soul intact.
Because at Maxwell's World, the attractions aren't just open. They're alive.
